00:00:54.330 --> 00:00:58.701
Let's play the Nico Burger Tower Game!

00:00:59.404 --> 00:01:02.256
What should I do?

00:01:02.256 --> 00:01:04.895
Stack a patty and a bun!

00:01:07.091 --> 00:01:11.899
