00:01:11.899 --> 00:01:12.882
Oh my god!

00:01:12.983 --> 00:01:13.925
Put the lettuce down

00:01:14.367 --> 00:01:15.762
Is this lettuce?

00:01:15.762 --> 00:01:16.553
Yep.

00:01:17.721 --> 00:01:19.443
Next is a patty!

00:01:24.545 --> 00:01:27.746
Stack a patty and a bun!

00:01:34.637 --> 00:01:38.875
Stack a bacon, an egg and a bun!	

00:01:40.808 --> 00:01:42.760
Ham! Ham!

00:01:43.217 --> 00:01:44.460
Egg!

00:01:49.568 --> 00:01:51.130
You lose!

00:01:52.266 --> 00:01:53.580
Akira lost!

00:01:53.817 --> 00:01:56.230
I didn't lose! The whole thing didn't fall down!

00:02:01.333 --> 00:02:05.920
Stack a lettuce, a bacon, a tomato and a bun!

00:02:06.083 --> 00:02:07.720
Lettuce

00:02:08.799 --> 00:02:10.400
Bacon

00:02:15.228 --> 00:02:17.990
Stack two patties and a bun!

00:02:18.560 --> 00:02:19.760
Which is the patty?

00:02:25.457 --> 00:02:28.120
Akira loses! The whole thing fell over.

00:02:34.223 --> 00:02:35.700
Your turn.

00:02:48.401 --> 00:02:50.070
I win!

00:02:50.068 --> 00:02:52.180
(Kanna wants to try stacking them all)

00:02:52.175 --> 00:02:53.420
Only two left!

00:03:08.025 --> 00:03:09.980
